    v1 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.74 - v1 + 0.38)) / ((v2 + 0.27 / v1 + 0.41) + (tmp + 0.50 * v0 + 0.63)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp))
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v1 = ((v0 / (v2 + 0.56 * tmp + 0.53)) * wp.cos((v0 + 0.66 * v0 + 0.24)))
    v1 = v0
